Detailed Description

cvmx_gser::_refclk_sel

This register selects the reference clock. These registers are reset by hardware only during chip cold reset. The values of the CSR fields in these registers do not change during chip warm or soft resets.

Not used with GSER6, GSER7, and GSER8.
